IMAPAccount gmail
Host imap.gmail.com
User stevan.antoine@gmail.com
PassCmd "gpg2 --quiet --for-your-eyes-only --no-tty --decrypt ~/.config/mu4e/stevan.antoine@gmail.com.gpg"
SSLType IMAPS
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt

IMAPStore gmail-remote
Account gmail

MaildirStore gmail-local
Subfolders Verbatim
Path ~/mail/
Inbox ~/mail/inbox

Channel gmail
Far :gmail-remote:
Near :gmail-local:
Patterns * ![Gmail]* "[Gmail]/Sent Mail" "[Gmail]/Starred" "[Gmail]/All Mail" "[Gmail]/Trash"
Create Both
SyncState *
